    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Collection Defined by Bold Statements",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The adidas x JAY3LLE capsule is more than just apparel - it\u2019s a powerful expression of the modern woman in sport. With a colour palette that features deep blacks, pure whites, and vibrant hues of purple, red, and pink, this collection offers a wide array of pieces, from performance-ready to fashion-forward.</p><h3><strong>Signature Pieces: Standout Designs in the Collection</strong></h3><p>The collection includes a range of apparel, footwear, and accessories that deliver style without compromising performance. Key pieces from the line include:</p><ul><li><strong>Bomber Jacket</strong>: A sleek layering piece with a full-zip design, 3-stripe accents, and an attached hood. The jacket also features subtle branding on the chest and a large embroidered adidas x JAY3LLE graphic across the back, combining sporty elegance with modern style.</li><li><strong>Pleated Skort</strong>: Combining elegance and functionality, this skort features adidas\u2019 performance materials and a chic removable pouch belt, giving it a unique and polished aesthetic. It\u2019s the perfect fusion of form and function for the modern golfer.</li><li><strong>CODECHAOS JAY3LLE High-Top Golf Shoe</strong>: The crown jewel of the collection, this ultra-high-top performance shoe breaks away from traditional golf footwear. Built on adidas\u2019 CODECHAOS platform, the shoe features a futuristic design with perforated leather detailing, a buckle and tee holder, BOOST cushioning, and a waterproof upper. It\u2019s a bold statement that challenges the very concept of golf footwear.</li></ul><h3><strong>Additional Collection Highlights</strong></h3><p>The capsule features a wide range of other pieces designed to complete the look, including:</p><ul><li><strong>PRIMEKNIT Sweatshirt</strong>: A fashionable yet functional crew neck with branding that bridges the gap between sport and streetwear.</li><li><strong>Long-Sleeve Form-Fitting Mock Neck Layer</strong>: A stylish layering piece with 3-Stripes detailing along the arms.</li><li><strong>Full-Zip Wind Gilet</strong>: An elegant yet sporty gilet designed to keep players comfortable in changing conditions.</li></ul><p>Accessories such as hats, headbands, and socks complete the capsule, ensuring that every aspect of a golfer\u2019s wardrobe is covered.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
