    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Driving Force: Women in Golf",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The adidas x JAY3LLE capsule isn\u2019t just about fashion; it\u2019s about a movement that reflects the growing influence of women in golf. With more women taking up the sport, there is a shift in the culture of golf - one that embraces inclusivity, style, and performance.</p><p><strong>Linn Grant</strong>, a rising star in women\u2019s golf and an adidas athlete, has been pivotal in bringing this collection to life. She will debut select pieces from the adidas x JAY3LLE collection at the prestigious <strong>AIG Women\u2019s Open at St. Andrews</strong>. Her involvement highlights the collection\u2019s focus on high performance and showcases how fashion and sport can blend seamlessly on the biggest stages in golf.</p><p><em>\u201cI\u2019ve always taken a personal interest in fashion outside of the course, so this capsule is one I\u2019m really excited about,\u201d</em> Grant says. <em>\u201cThese silhouettes will inspire a lot of women to wear something that will provide them with energy and positivity whenever they play.\u201d</em></p><h2><strong>A Deeper Connection: The JAY3LLE Brand</strong></h2><p>JAY3LLE is a creative extension of Johan and Blue Lindeberg\u2019s belief in cross-generational creativity and fashion\u2019s power to unite people. The father-daughter duo founded JAY3LLE to create a lifestyle community that spans generations and borders, connecting people through their shared love for sport, fashion, and creativity.</p><p>Johan Lindeberg explains, <em>\u201cWe believe that now, more than ever, it\u2019s time to combine fashion and sports. JAY3LLE is a new lifestyle community where we combine our two personalities and networks.\u201d</em></p><p>The capsule represents more than just a collection; it\u2019s a fusion of creativity, culture, and sport that encourages a new generation of golfers to express themselves on the course.</p><h2><strong>The Future of Golf Fashion</strong></h2><p>The adidas x JAY3LLE capsule is not just about creating stylish golf apparel. It\u2019s about pushing the boundaries of what golf fashion can be. This collaboration represents the evolution of golf style, bringing in influences from streetwear and high fashion while staying true to the performance needs of athletes.</p><p>For Johan and Blue Lindeberg, this collection is a continuation of a lifelong passion for fashion and sport. It\u2019s a step toward a future where golf is embraced not just as a sport, but as a culture - one that celebrates individuality, creativity, and community.</p><p><em>\u201cThe new generation loves golf and enjoys dressing individually on the golf course,\u201d</em> Johan Lindeberg says. <em>\u201cWith JAY3LLE, we want to be part of the new movement and the new generation in golf.\u201d</em></p>"
          }
        }
      },
